NEW settings :
--------------

-We replace @Repository with @RepositoryRestController : instead of build and calling apis from rest with requests , you need just to call such many methods without define it
                                                         for exemple : if you have class User , then http://localhost:8080/users with a get request will give you a list of all users
                                                                                                http://localhost:808/users/seach/? gives you a user
